Author: stupidthrowawaynya
Text: thank you :< i completely get that. i’m back to such a toxic mindset after beginning to recover. like,, it’s like “i ate one tiny carrot, i am going to be fat and disgusting for the entirety of my life and i will restrict for 3 days straight now”. i’m here if you need anything, okay? we’re in this together

Author: RaniBlue
Text: Yeah, I know how you feel. Lately I've been feeling awful about myself with crazy guilt after I eat, even if it's my only food of the day and it's completely fine calorie-wise. This disease is a bitch.  You're not alone, boo.
